 Magnus looked at his wrist. He saw what his council had begum. A pred 
empire. And now he would set them back a little. His compartment opened. He 
pressed the red button and it was done.
   *at the council base* the base shook. the procedure was final with no 
override. In the matter of three seconds the base was dicenercrated. Sphink 
was in the control room and was vaproazied. Before the explosion all the 
doors locked down immediatly encloseing all who was in it. 

Magnus looked into the glass like armour of his. Staring at his face. Nowing 
he did what he had to do.......

--part1_18.7530a4f.278f6c0f_boundary
